      <refnamediv>
        <refname>mts_connect
</refname>
        <refpurpose> connects Virtuoso server to MS DTC. 
</refpurpose>
      </refnamediv>
      <refsynopsisdiv>
        <funcsynopsis xml:id="fsyn_mts_connect">
          <funcprototype xml:id="fproto_mts_connect">
            <funcdef>
              <function>mts_connect
</function>
            </funcdef>
            <paramdef choice="opt">in 
<parameter>reconnect
</parameter>

   integer
</paramdef>
          </funcprototype>
        </funcsynopsis>
      </refsynopsisdiv>
      <refsect1 xml:id="desc_mts_connect">
        <title>Description
</title>
        <para> If reconnect flag is set to non-zero value then forces Virtuoso to connect even it have been connected already. Returns zero if succeeds. If MS DTC service is not available (W2K) or MTS is not running (NT4.0) signals error with code "MX000". 
</para>
